creator: HealthMetrics Sdn Bhd
descriptionHtml:
Medical benefits simplified. Get updates on your medical benefits from your company, search for panel healthcare providers and get directions to them.

HealthMetrics employee app allows you to:

- Verify your identity with the mobile app at our panel healthcare providers,
- Locate the nearest panel healthcare provider from your current location,
- Check your medical limits,
- Get real-time updates on medical charges & MC given by healthcare provider, and
- Get claim breakdowns on previous medical expenditure.

It's a new way of experiencing better health care. Having trouble finding a doctor is the last thing you would want when you're having a headache. With the HealthMetrics, spare the trouble and locate a clinic with ease.

HealthMetrics also gives you real-time updates on any changes to panel healthcare providers. Unsure whether the nearest GP is one of our healthcare providers? Check the app and you'll get your confirmation.

Problems logging into the app? Email us at support@healthmetrics.co or call us at +60 3-7661 6229.
